- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possibility as the paper proposes a method to improve the performance of a system.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions aligning fingerprints to locations.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also less likely but possible as the paper discusses measurement fluctuations and the impact on the fingerprinting system.
